Photo album
-----------

Set up:

Edit the conf.json file as follows

  "enabled": true,

- "duration":   The number of seconds to show the photo
- "extensions": A list of extensions that will be included when searching for photos, ["jpg", "png"]
- "folders":    A list of folders to search for photos (not recursive)
            ["/home/pi/RPi-InfoScreen-Kivy-master/images",
            "/home/pi/Desktop"
            ]
            
